{"tid":1725201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】『政府答應五大訴求，才是回覆平靜的最快方法』","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T18:26:32.000Z","uid":90601,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c56f307c2a5f7c31f888417c9bbd841d17e078bf","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"抗爭已經關鍵時候，連九大校長都出聲明叫政府用政治方式解決問題<br />\n港島區今個禮拜破天荒日日「和你lunch」，民意前所未有咁強<br />\n政府仲on99日日係打民意戰，將個因果扭曲成「抗爭＞混亂＝五大訴求係要挾」<br />\n但實際上，我地要重新聲明因果係「政府唔理五大訴求＞抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n淨係得勇武手足擋黑警係唔夠，和理非一定要重新上場脅逼政府<br />\n不戰而屈人之兵，用盡民意令政府屈服，先係性價比最高既抗爭方法<br />\n見到文宣組出左文宣，請盡量係依個周末用盡力廣傳：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2xdTA9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2xdTA9b.jpg&h=7de6df28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Bd00AU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Bd00AU.jpg&h=9c5ba039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqCAPug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqCAPug.jpg&h=286736ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aou7FAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAou7FAY.jpg&h=0d178d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外見到個幾得意 純粹share：<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vvhw7fZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvvhw7fZ.jpg&h=c5f53c95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0052ee7da5f8d5c893d9aad9e0e134ee1b33161","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae48733ebe5a1a466ff8977e1c758acf9edcdea","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:22:09