ll.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a57f7deafc5987076a22837c9266af2403788d","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38652f7742af30c9343fc4ab688f37d743a0d9a6","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a2476a90428b0a73ada3b7365e1bcb3bb1a9bc","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95afe11d919e6f8e1db74839e5f4d7407b4a073e","tid":1725201,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果無修改手足可以擺上facebook/instagram手動轉貼:<br />\n手動傳!!</span><br />\n<br />\n香港市民回應政府發言<br />\n*************************************************<br />\n本星期香港市民為五大訴求連續五日以不同方式抗爭，展現無比決心，望政府認清香港人無法被槍彈打壓，不割蓆，抗爭之心不死的事實。而政府於此星期內不但沒有正面積極回應民意，更強攻大學校園，縱容黑社會暴力襲擊市民；另一方面刻意製造抗爭者內鬥，又連同建制政黨組織地方武裝鎮壓，以圖歪曲民意消耗抗爭力量。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民於本星期抗爭展示力量之餘，更進一步顯示保家衛港及永不割席的決心，現決定給予政府周末兩天時間，答應五大訴求及正面處理警方濫暴問題，還市民應有權利及公義，政治解決政治問題，以免全港經濟更嚴重受損及進一步有市民傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n此等機會難逢，政府應慎重考慮，勿一錯再錯，將香港推往不歸路。否則，香港人定當於星期一再次發動規模更大的抗爭行動。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年11月15日（星期五）"},{"pid":"bccfa3a984e603ec2141e708e51c91224e6c61c1","tid":1725201,"uid":241101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"唔爭取返和理支持<br />\n就冇人控制勇武<br />\n社會就唔會回復安寧"},{"pid":"0f01a225de693f4bc032422afbc658bcf1b31fc1","tid":1725201,"uid":186800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bccfa3a984e603ec2141e708e51c91224e6c61c1","tid":1725201,"uid":241101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"唔爭取返和理支持<br />\n就冇人控制勇武<br />\n社會就唔會回復安寧"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"而家都無人控制到<br />\n成日話不割根本就係助長佢地為所欲為"},{"pid":"9c6163aa6e9d5676053317cde35294271e399636","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f01a225de693f4bc032422afbc658bcf1b31fc1","tid":1725201,"uid":186800,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bccfa3a984e603ec2141e708e51c91224e6c61c1","tid":1725201,"uid":241101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"唔爭取返和理支持<br />\n就冇人控制勇武<br />\n社會就唔會回復安寧"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"而家都無人控制到<br />\n成日話不割根本就係助長佢地為所欲為"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:49:52.000Z","msg":"嚴禁互屌 不指責 各自努力"},{"pid":"395cb948a52253becbeab2f4da75c740c024460b","tid":1725201,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3707d653aab50ecaca38db5f8fdbfc800af1249d","tid":1725201,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"林鄭最驚全民天光開花，最希望示威者夜晚集中一點打陣地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"280f4c9709b98312a0383b996c0a1d003ed7cccb","tid":1725201,"uid":186800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6163aa6e9d5676053317cde35294271e399636","tid":1725201,"uid":906